title: Percentage of team/marketing tokens
body: The team requires a token share for further development, marketing and to participate in the upcoming LGE events. If team funding is left short the timetable and the future LGE events of the project could suffer. We have decided to make the community decide the percentage of the tokens the team should keep. The team's tokens would be locked into permanent liquidity in the upcoming liquidity generation events.
author: 0xF0CD3b969C7da9117292f424E1472999Ed6Fd40e
